
Parts of this windowing model have been implemented.

Click  - xoff, yoff, selnotadjust, icon handle
Menu   - xoff, yoff, icon handle
Redraw - redraw x0,y0,x1,x1
Open   - x,y, sx,sy, behind -1/-2/-3
         CHANGE: x0,y0, x1,y1, sx,sy, behind -1/-2/-3
         Reason: We need to know how big to open it :-)
Close  - flags
         (1 | 4) + &1000 [shift]
Enter  - .
Leave  - .
Key    - char, icon handle
Focus  - gainnotlost, icon

Iconize- ?
Help   - x, y, icon

Save      dragged to somewhere
Load      dragged onto us
Dragging  dragged to us
Info      iconise
